         <div xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625"><!-- p5l1-r5 -->
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Hd1e108">Rubrica 5</head>
            <head xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Hd1e111" type="question-title">De spe et desperatione</head>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e114">
               De spe et desperatione. Rubrica. 5.
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e119">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e116">SAlomon in prouerbiis
               capitulo 13.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e125">Spes quae
               Idiffertur affligat animam.</quote> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e131"> 
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e129">27. capitulo.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e133">Ne
               glorieris in crastinum ignorans quid
               superuentura pariat dies.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e142">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e144">Regum libro 2. capitulo 2.</ref> ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e146">An ignoras quod 
               periculosa sit desperatio.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e152">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e156">ARistoteles rethoricorum libro 1. capitulo 20.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e156">Speranti 
               consequitur fantasia aliqua eius quod sperat.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e162"> 
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e166">libro 2
               capitulo 16.</ref> ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e164">Iuuenes bone spei sunt. ¶ Iuuenes 
               propterea quod nondum in multis repulsam passi sunt
               uiuunt secundum plurima spei spes quidem futuri
               est memoria autem preteriti iuuenibus autem quod
               quidem futurum multum preteritum autem breue. 
               Iuuenes facile seductibiles sunt sperant enim 
               facile. Senes difficilis spei sunt propter 
               experientiam. plura enim eorum que fiunt mala sunt
               eueniunt enim multa indeterius.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e187">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e196">Iesus filius sirach in ecclesiastico capitulo 22.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e191">Ad
               amicum et si produxeris gladium ne desperes. est
               enim regressus ad amicum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e199">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e210">Oratius in epistolis. libro 1. epistola 4.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e203">Grata 
               superueniet que non sperabitur hora.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e209">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e222">TUllius inuectiuarum in catilinam libro 4. et finali.</ref>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e213">Spes sola hominem in miseriis consolari solet.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e220">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e235">Ouidius epistolarum. 2. epistola.</ref> ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e224">Quecumque ex 
               merito spes uenit equa uenit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e230">
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e247">epistola. 16.</ref>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e234">Fallitur augurio spes bona sepe suo</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e240">
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e259">Idem methamorphoseum libro 1.</ref>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e244">Spes tamen in dubio est.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e250">
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e271">libro. 9.</ref>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e254">Spes est que cupiarspes est qui pascat amantem</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e260">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e283">Idem de ponto libro 3. epistola 7. et antepenultimo.</ref>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e264">Spem iuuat amplecti que non iuuat irrita semper
               Et fieri cupias si qua futura putes.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e272">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e297">Quintilianus delcamationum. 7 declamatione.</ref>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e276">Nichil magis interesse hominum puto quam ut
               spes pro homine tam longa quam uita sit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e285">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e312">Seneca epistolarum ad lucillum. libro 2. epistola 3.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e289">Spes
               incerti boni nomen est.</quote> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e320">
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e322">libro 12. epistola 2. et finali.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e324">
               Diuitie insolentiam dant nichil est aliud 
               insolentia quam spes false magnitudinis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e299"> 
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e334">libro 18. epistola 1.</ref>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e301">O quanta dementia est spes longas inchoantium.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e313"> 
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e350">Idem declamationum libro 5. capitulo 1.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e315">Spes
               ultimum est aduersarum rerum solatium.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e321"> 
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e360">libro 9. capitulo 6. et finali.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e323">Concitatissima est rabies in 
               desperatione.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e331"> 
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e373">Idem de breuitate uite.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e333">Spes
               spem excitat ambitionem ambitio.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e339">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e386">Lucanus. libro 1.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e343">Spes saltem trepidas 
               mentes leuat.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e350">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e398">Ualerius maximus libro 6. titulo 9. et finali.</ref> ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e354">Stultum
               est perpetue infelicitati se damnare spemque
               ex incerto recte fouetur interdum certam in 
               desperationem conuertere.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e364">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e414">Statius thebaidos libro 2.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e368">Non grauior 
               mortalibus addita cura Spe ubi longa uenit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e374">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e426">Uegetius de re militari. libro 3. titulo 10.</ref> ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e378">Nemo 
               desperet fieri posse que facta sunt.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e384"> 
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e436">libro 3. titulo
               23</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e386">Ex desperatione crescit audacia et cum
               spei nichil est sumit arma formido.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e394">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e451">Augustinus in epigrammatibus 
               prosperi epigramma 86</ref> ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e398">Non est desperandum de 
               malis sed pro ipsis ut boni fiant potius 
               supplicandum quia numerus sanctorum semper est
               auctus de numero impiorum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e410">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e471">CAto. capitulo 3.</ref> ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e414">Spem retine spes una
               hominem nec morte reliquit.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e421">
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e483">capitulo. 5. et finali.</ref>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e425">In aduersis melius sperare memento.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e431">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e495">Boetius. libro diuisionum</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e435">Quis non 
               uideat plurimum ad bonarum artium 
               defectum ualere si apud mentes hominum numquam
               sit desperatio discendi.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e445">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e511">Cassiodorus epistolarum libro 4. epistola 25.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e449">In ipsis
               conatibus egra languescunt que meritorum
               presumptionibus non inuuantur.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e457">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e525">Isydorus in synonima <sic>solliloquiorum</sic> libro 1. capitulo.</ref>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e461">Desperatio auget peccatum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e467">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e540">Uersificator fabularum esopi. 29 fabula.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e471">Sic
               timeat quicumque timet ne molle timoris.
               Spe careat grauis est spe fugiente timor.
               ¶ Speret qui metuit morituros uiuere uidi
               Spe duce uicturos spe moriente mori.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e483">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e559">Auctor libro qui dicitur pamphylus. capitulo 1.</ref>
               ¶ <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e487">Spes reficit dominum fallit et ipsa suum.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e494">
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e571">capitulo. 13.</ref>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e498">Obstitit interdum factis fortuna uirorum
               Propositumque suo non sinit esse loco.</quote> 
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e512">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e592">capitulo. 36.</ref>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e516">Desperare nocet uotum labor improbus implet.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e600">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e604">capitulo 37.</ref>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e608">Sorte sub ambigua spes et labor omnis habetur.
               Crescit principio spes tamen ipsa bono.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e528">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e618">Baldo. 11 fabula.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e532">Hic ope uirtutis spes
               est ubi nulla salutis.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e538">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e630">Gualterius de castellione libro 7.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e542">Spes in 
               dubiis semper comes optima rebus.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e548">
               ¶ <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e643">Iacobus beneuentanus. capitulo 56.</ref> <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e552">Spes 
               bona mortales fallere sepe solet.</quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-d1e558">
               <ref xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Rd1e655">Auctor libelli de moribus medicorum. capitulo 11.</ref>
               <quote xml:id="bHY6yh-d93625-Qd1e562">Spes mulios decipit. atque
               Hec eadem reficit implet: et euacuat.</quote>
            </p>
         </div>
